WEBVTT

00:06:30.325 --> 00:06:34.880
Now just imagine that sentiment
with a machine that can outthink you

00:06:34.904 --> 00:06:36.747
and is heavily armed.

00:06:36.771 --> 00:06:38.282
(Laughter)

00:06:39.074 --> 00:06:40.275
The result?

00:06:40.976 --> 00:06:42.178
Absolutely.

00:06:42.202 --> 00:06:43.658
(Laughter)

00:06:46.973 --> 00:06:50.217
What we need to do before we perfect
artificial intelligence

00:06:50.241 --> 00:06:52.428
is perfect artificial emotions.

00:06:52.793 --> 00:06:56.703
That way, we can teach
the robots or machines

00:06:56.727 --> 00:06:59.208
how to love us unconditionally,

00:06:59.232 --> 00:07:03.757
so that when they figure out
that the only real problem on this planet